# write tests of svelte components

- before each test, use `mount()` and `vi.mock()`
- after each test, use `unmount()` and `vi.clearAllMocks()`
- mount target component to `document.body`
- if user says "write tests", then write tests to be. test will fail, but ok. do not edit the target.

